 {"file_name": "4.png", "id": "1193974355271044", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75272208_1193974358604377_1156306078450200288_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=2mJsbhSkvdQQ7kNvgEHw7X2&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDUIdpGDvwnM6nflQI176MnT-A9KkMkKIe_xnWyq3_ghg&oe=677A65E0"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Echo Eyes", "keywords": [], "long_description": "# EchoEyes: Your AI-Powered Companion for Visual Understanding\n\n# \ud83d\udc41\ufe0f See the World Through AI\n\nWelcome to EchoEyes, an innovative AI-powered app designed to empower individuals with visual impairments. Using cutting-edge technology and intuitive hand gestures, EchoEyes helps you understand your surroundings and navigate the world with confidence.\n{1233961281090920}\n## \ud83c\udf1f Key Features\n- **Gesture-Based Interface**: Simple hand movements control the app, ensuring ease of use.\n- **Real-Time Environment Description**: Get instant audio descriptions of your surroundings.\n- **Obstacle Detection**: Receive timely alerts about potential hazards in your path.\n\n\n## \ud83d\udd27 How It Works\n- Activate EchoEyes with a simple gesture.\n- Explore your environment using intuitive hand movements.\n- Listen to clear, concise audio descriptions and alerts.\n\n## \ud83d\ude80 Benefits\n\n- **Enhanced Independence**: Navigate unfamiliar spaces with greater confidence.\n- **Improved Safety**: Stay aware of potential dangers in your surroundings.\n- **Expanded Access**: Interact with visual information previously out of reach.\n- **Seamless Integration**: Fits naturally into your daily routine.\n\n## \ud83d\udca1 Perfect For\n\n- Individuals with visual impairments\n- Those experiencing gradual vision loss\n- Anyone seeking an extra layer of environmental awareness", "short_description": "Welcome to EchoEyes, an AI-powered app designed for the blind. With just simple hand gestures, it helps 